headline: 2 mortars at Gush Katif
description: Two people were treated for shock following a mortar attack on the Gaza Strip settlement of Neve Dekalim. Gush Katif officials said three mortars landed near the settlement Monday.(Roni Sofer)
articleBody: Two people were treated for shock following a mortar attack on the Gaza Strip settlement of Neve Dekalim. Gush Katif officials said three mortars landed near the settlement Monday.(Roni Sofer)
